Using the Internet

Legal Documents

   On October 3, 2001, the Commission issued a Notice of Proposed
   Rulemaking on Use of the Internet for Campaign Activity. The Commission
   also had published a Notice of Inquiry [11/5/1999] on this subject. For
   more information on this rulemaking and to see all the legal documents
   go to Recent and Ongoing Rulemaking/Regulations (Federal Register
   Notices).

